<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Hadith Daily - Register</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.7/dist/tailwind.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-100">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen pt-6 mb-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 max-w-md">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Sign up to your account</h1>

        <form action="/register" method="POST" class="mb-8">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <label
              for="name"
              class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-2"
              >Name:</label
            >
            <input
              type="text"
              name="name"
              id="name"
              required
              class="appearance-none border rounded w-full py-2 px-3 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <label
              for="email"
              class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-2"
              >Email:</label
            >
            <input
              type="email"
              name="email"
              id="email"
              required
              class="appearance-none border rounded w-full py-2 px-3 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <label
              for="password"
              class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-2"
              >Password:</label
            >
            <input
              type="password"
              name="password"
              id="password"
              required
              class="appearance-none border rounded w-full py-2 px-3 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <button
              type="submit"
              class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-opacity-50"
            >
              Register
            </button>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 m-1">Already have an account? <a href="/login" class="text-blue-500 font-semibold">Login</a></p>
        </form>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Join us as we embark on a journey to explore the profound teachings of
          the Prophet Muhammad ï·º and learn how to apply them in our daily lives.
          Each day, receive a new Hadith that will enlighten your mind and touch
          your heart.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-semibold">
          Stay connected to the wisdom of Islam and let the Hadiths guide you
          towards a path of righteousness, compassion, and spiritual growth.
        </p>
      </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
